A:  I think I probably said. "She's probably in love with you and"--
that's the impression I got, that Paula was in love with him and I 
think wanted to have kids with him. 
 
Q:  And what, if anything, did O.J. Simpson say? 
 
A:  That he already had his kids and all that; not sure if she was the 
