said, "Kato?" 
I said, "Yeah."  He said, "You forgot to turn the jacuzzi off," and 
he was at the door of my front room. 
And I came to the door, I went, "Oh, God."  So I was almost 
getting ready to do it, and he had said he had shut them off already. 
 
