A:  Well, I felt as if it wasn't up to me to say, "Hey, let's go here."  
It wasn't my call to make.  I invited myself, so I wasn't going to 
say, "Oh, O.J.  let 's go to this restaurant."  It was his call.  So 
wherever the car was taking us, I was there for the ride. 
 
Q:  When did you discover where you were going to eat? 
 
A:  When we pulled into McDonald's. 
 
Q:  So Mr. Simpson at no time asked you what you would like to 
