Q:  He looked where? 
 
A:  There is a clock. 
 
Q:  Up on the wall. 
 
A:  On the wall. 
 
Q:  And he said what when he saw that clock? 
 
A:  "Is that the right time?" or "My God, is it that late?" or--it was 
