their relationship. 
I said.  "No.  I don't have a problem.  I'll go." 
And I--the part of it was O.J. saying to me.  "Just tell the truth."  
And some of the other dialogue.  I just can't remember.  I don't 
remember it being very long. 
And then I remember going back to the house for some--at some 
