said, "I'll show you. I'll prove to you that." 
 
And then she said, "I don't care." And so I didn't know exactly 
what it was about, if that was from the party. so I just kept going, 
"What happened that this is going on?" 
 
Q: It was just kind of sudden that it happened? 
 
A: Yeah. It happened, Like I said. 15 minutes, I think, into the 
party. 
 
