A: I didn't know it. 
 
Q: No one told you that? 
 
A: No. I know there was something going on with Marcus, but I 
think Marcus is married, so I didn't believe it. 
 
Q: Who did you hear it from? 
 
A: Oh, I knew he got married. 
 
Q: Who did you hear it from that something was going on with 
Marcus? 
 
A: I believe it was Cora. I pretty much talked to only Cora after 
anything had happened because Cora was the only person I really 
talked to. 
 
Q: What do you mean, "after anything had happened"? 
 
A: After the murders. 
 
Q: Your conversations after the murders were with Cora? 
 
A: Yes. 
 
Q: And you think Cora told you that Nicole had been seeing 
Marcus? 
 
A: I believe that at some point also I heard in May that there was a 
