A: They were like a cheap kind of Doc Martens--not Doc Martens, 
but like a cheaper brand.  
 
Q: Okay. Rubber soles? 
 
A: I think so. 
 
Q: Do you still have them? 
 
A: Plastic. Rubber. I think I have one of them. When there was a 
move a lot of my stuff wasn't ever accounted for. 
 
