harmful, that they had agreed in Cabo San Lucas that they would 
not do that. That's one of the reasons why they continued to try to 
reconcile because they had come to an agreement in Cabo that they 
needed to compromise on their boundaries and that was against the 
agreement, and I also said to him that I didn't appreciate being put 
in that position, and he told me that she had told him that she was 
with Marcus Allen, against her will and that he just lost it. He felt - 
he said that he told Nicole that that was the one thing she should 
have never done, that if he ever saw her with Marcus again, he 
didn't know what he would do. 
 
Q. That's what O.J. Simpson told you? 
 
A. Yes. 
 
