A. He did it in everybody's presence. 
 
Q. But you saw him do it? 
 
A. Yes. 
 
Q. This is October 1993? 
 
A. Yes, it is. 
 
Q. O.J. Simpson denied using cocaine at all in 1993. Would that be 
