and O.J. Simpson? 
 
A. Christian - I had introduced Christian to O.J. when Nicole and 
O.J. reconciled, and that was, they - due to the fact we were always 
going out, having dinners together, they became acquainted. 
During, I would say, from the time in Laguna Beach, which was 
July, they had become fairly well acquainted and Christian was 
now, had now considered O.J. his friend. He was very protective of 
O.J. and he admired O.J. 
 
Q. What was their business connection? 
 
A. Their business connection was O.J. had called Christian during 
