A. He answered the phone many times when O.J. Simpson called 
and he was there many times when I had conversations with him. 
Due to the fact that O.J. Simpson used to call me at 1 or 2 o'clock 
in the morning, Christian typically used to answer the phone and 
hand it to me. 
 
Q. Just staying with that for the moment, were there ever any 
