In a stunning development, the psychiatrist who has treated Erik Menendez since his arrest admitted that he doctored his notes of those sessions at the direction of defense attorney Leslie Abramson.</P>

<P><A HREF="pp01.html">Penalty Phase: Week 1</A><BR>
The penalty phase of the trial opens with Erik and Lyle Menendez's aunt pleading with the jury to spare her nephews' lives.</P>

