The jury deliberates for three days without reaching a verdict.</P>

<P><A HREF="ts20.html">Trial Summary: Week 20</A><BR>
The defense presents its closing arguments. The jury starts deliberating.</P>

<P><A HREF="ts19.html">Trial Summary: Week 19</A><BR>
Prosecutor David Conn presents his closing argument.</P>

<P><A HREF="ts18.html">Trial Summary: Week 18</A><BR>
The evidence phase of the trial ends.</P>

