<p><H2>Bowman v. Calvert (7/93)</H2>

Patricia Bowman, the Florida woman who accused William Kennedy Smith of rape, sought a restraining order against reporter Robert Calvert. She claimed that he repeatedly called her, questioned her neighbors, drove by her home and asked her for dates. Calvert's attorney contended his client was just doing his job.<P>

<b>Verdict</b><br>
The parties reached an out-of-court settlement.<P>

