http://www.courttv.com:80/casefiles/verdicts/goetz.html 199.29.97.40 19970108063339 text/html 3755
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 06:43:16 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 01-Nov-96 15:25:16 GMT
Content-length: 3564
