HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 06:52:18 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 06-Dec-96 22:22:31 GMT
Content-length: 6182
Content-type: text/html
