<P><h2>Victory v. City of Murfreesboro, Tennessee (4/96)</h2>
An elderly couple sued the city after a fleeing suspect's car crashed into their vehicle and injured them during a police chase. They claimed the police were negligent and contributed to the accident by chasing a suspected drunk driver. The defense claimed the police officers were carrying out their responsibility to safeguard the public.<p>

<b>Verdict</b><br>
The judge found for the city.<p>

